1
00:01:25,472 --> 00:01:29,792
=Lost You Forever S2=

2
00:01:30,132 --> 00:01:32,880
=Episode 16=

3
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,801
Marrying Nian
will make you a bit happier.

4
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:39,600
After all, you watched her grow up.

5
00:01:41,041 --> 00:01:42,081
In your heart,

6
00:01:43,081 --> 00:01:45,721
she must be different from
those women from the Zijin Peak.

7
00:01:46,121 --> 00:01:47,761
Nian is different from them.

8
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:49,001
But it doesn't mean

9
00:01:49,001 --> 00:01:51,161
I want to marry her.

10
00:02:04,001 --> 00:02:05,200
Your marriage to Nian would quell

11
00:02:05,801 --> 00:02:07,361
the strife between our two kingdoms.

12
00:02:08,081 --> 00:02:10,521
Moreover, Nian is sincere.

13
00:02:11,081 --> 00:02:12,560
And you know she likes you

14
00:02:12,881 --> 00:02:14,801
more than any other women.

15
00:02:17,441 --> 00:02:18,321
Have you ever considered

16
00:02:18,321 --> 00:02:19,200
what I truly feel?

17
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,920
You've only ever thought about Nian.

18
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,361
Nian wants to marry me.

19
00:02:23,920 --> 00:02:24,680
You think

20
00:02:24,721 --> 00:02:25,521
that I already have

21
00:02:25,521 --> 00:02:26,721
so many women,

22
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,721
so one more woman

23
00:02:27,721 --> 00:02:29,200
doesn't really matter, right?

24
00:02:29,961 --> 00:02:31,161
What are you talking about?

25
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,441
I just think

26
00:02:33,801 --> 00:02:34,881
if you could previously marry

27
00:02:34,881 --> 00:02:36,560
those women to win over those clans,

28
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,881
why can't you marry Nian?

29
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,200
Is she in any way inferior to them?

30
00:02:45,640 --> 00:02:46,801
Why are you looking at me?

31
00:02:47,961 --> 00:02:48,640
Back then,

32
00:02:49,001 --> 00:02:50,241
when you married Chenrong Xinyue,

33
00:02:50,241 --> 00:02:51,200
you were all elated.

34
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:53,321
What's wrong with marrying Nian now?

35
00:02:54,081 --> 00:02:55,161
Why so reluctant?

36
00:02:56,881 --> 00:02:58,721
When was I ever elated?

37
00:03:00,361 --> 00:03:01,640
Did you see that?

38
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,640
Tell me

39
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:04,840
how I was ever elated.

40
00:03:07,881 --> 00:03:09,241
I didn't see it with my own eyes,

41
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:10,640
but back in the day,

42
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,920
when you married Chenrong Xinyue,

43
00:03:12,521 --> 00:03:13,961
the people of Haoling all discussed it.

44
00:03:14,321 --> 00:03:15,081
So many people

45
00:03:15,081 --> 00:03:16,560
saw you in high spirits.

46
00:03:16,961 --> 00:03:17,760
Xiaoyao,

47
00:03:19,361 --> 00:03:21,521
anyone can say so, but you...

48
00:03:22,241 --> 00:03:24,081
How could you?

49
00:03:27,441 --> 00:03:28,029
Cang Xuan,

50
00:03:28,601 --> 00:03:29,840
just be drunk

51
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,161
in front of all the guests from Dahuang

52
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,721
and the officials from both kingdoms

53
00:03:32,721 --> 00:03:33,441
tomorrow.

54
00:03:33,441 --> 00:03:35,361
Xiling Jiuyao, let me tell you.

55
00:03:35,881 --> 00:03:37,760
I felt very sad
every time I got married,

56
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:39,321
especially when I married

57
00:03:39,321 --> 00:03:40,881
Chenrong Xinyue.

58
00:03:41,521 --> 00:03:43,001
I even hate myself

59
00:03:43,001 --> 00:03:44,001
and hate you too.

60
00:03:47,001 --> 00:03:47,961
If you are drunk again,

61
00:03:48,441 --> 00:03:49,120
I will hit you.

62
00:03:51,721 --> 00:03:52,400
I'm serious.

63
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,801
I don't want any of those women.

64
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,001
I just want...

65
00:04:14,480 --> 00:04:15,280
I just want...

66
00:04:35,601 --> 00:04:36,240
Cang Xuan,

67
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,481
what is wrong with you?

68
00:04:40,201 --> 00:04:41,201
Before,

69
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,840
I could always tell
what you were thinking.

70
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,321
But this time, I have no idea at all.

71
00:04:49,721 --> 00:04:50,520
I admit

72
00:04:52,001 --> 00:04:53,601
I did only think about Nian.

73
00:04:53,641 --> 00:04:54,840
I didn't consider you.

74
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,641
Because in my heart,

75
00:04:59,280 --> 00:04:59,881
I feel

76
00:05:01,721 --> 00:05:04,080
you care more about the whole world

77
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,641
and the political landscape,

78
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,481
and care less about other things.

79
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:42,601
Which of these two pendants
do you prefer?

80
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:44,881
Whichever.

81
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,441
Then at the wedding ceremony tomorrow,

82
00:05:52,721 --> 00:05:54,400
which color of lipstick
do you want to apply?

83
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,080
Vermilion,

84
00:05:56,161 --> 00:05:56,881
silvery red,

85
00:05:57,041 --> 00:05:57,641
scarlet,

86
00:05:57,721 --> 00:05:58,280
rose red,

87
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,360
begonia red

88
00:05:59,481 --> 00:06:00,120
or peach red?

89
00:06:01,201 --> 00:06:01,800
Whichever.

90
00:06:04,041 --> 00:06:04,800
Why do you

91
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,041
always reply "whichever"?

92
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,560
My dream has come true.

93
00:06:09,441 --> 00:06:10,013
I'm happy.

94
00:06:13,721 --> 00:06:15,721
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

95
00:06:23,001 --> 00:06:24,761
I've never seen a bride like you.

96
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,161
Then what do you think a bride

97
00:06:26,161 --> 00:06:27,080
should be like?

98
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:29,321
If one day,

99
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:30,601
I can marry Cang Xuan,

100
00:06:30,881 --> 00:06:32,161
I will definitely be nervous.

101
00:06:32,601 --> 00:06:33,881
I'll also be a bit scared

102
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:35,080
that I'm not pretty enough.

103
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:39,120
From accessories to the color of rouge,

104
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,761
I will pick everything personally.

105
00:06:40,761 --> 00:06:41,680
I will look forward

106
00:06:41,721 --> 00:06:43,080
to my future with him.

107
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:01,981
Nian,

108
00:07:03,161 --> 00:07:04,161
are you happy?

109
00:07:08,321 --> 00:07:09,400
I used to think

110
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,041
if one day,

111
00:07:11,041 --> 00:07:12,321
I could marry Cang Xuan,

112
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,520
I would surely be overjoyed.

113
00:07:15,441 --> 00:07:18,080
But now my dream has come true,

114
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,120
and I am not as happy as I had imagined.

115
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:22,240
If you have regrets,

116
00:07:22,641 --> 00:07:23,960
I will issue an edict at once

117
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,560
to cancel tomorrow's wedding.

118
00:07:29,041 --> 00:07:30,481
Now all the people of Dahuang know

119
00:07:30,864 --> 00:07:32,800
that I will be married
to the King of Xiyan tomorrow.

120
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:35,041
The Four Great Clans,

121
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,441
Haoling's four tribes,

122
00:07:37,201 --> 00:07:38,400
the clans of the Central Plains,

123
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,321
and the old clans of Xiyan

124
00:07:40,881 --> 00:07:42,120
all gather at Wushen Mountain.

125
00:07:43,001 --> 00:07:43,881
The wedding

126
00:07:44,601 --> 00:07:46,321
can't be canceled casually.

127
00:07:47,201 --> 00:07:48,240
I am the King of Haoling.

128
00:07:48,921 --> 00:07:50,001
So I have the final say.

129
00:07:50,601 --> 00:07:52,321
You just consider
whether you want to marry or not.

130
00:07:52,601 --> 00:07:54,680
Leave the rest to me.

131
00:07:55,201 --> 00:07:56,560
Kings should keep their word.

132
00:07:57,161 --> 00:07:59,680
Aren't you afraid of
being ridiculed by the people?

133
00:08:11,001 --> 00:08:12,280
Compared to your lifelong happiness,

134
00:08:12,441 --> 00:08:14,560
the people's scorn

135
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,721
is nothing.

136
00:08:22,201 --> 00:08:24,560
All the clans gather at Wushen Mountain.

137
00:08:25,520 --> 00:08:26,321
It is just good.

138
00:08:27,120 --> 00:08:28,800
Presumably, each clan has sent out

139
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,280
their most outstanding offsprings.

140
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:33,680
Among them are certainly
many outstanding young men.

141
00:08:34,441 --> 00:08:36,281
You can choose an ideal husband

142
00:08:36,441 --> 00:08:37,800
among them.

143
00:08:43,920 --> 00:08:45,001
It is not

144
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:47,360
just mine and Cang Xuan's wedding.

145
00:08:47,641 --> 00:08:49,680
It also concerns the peace
of the Dahuang.

146
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,680
Father,

147
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:53,881
if you cancel it

148
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,360
and change the groom casually,

149
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,641
aren't you afraid of causing
chaos in Dahuang?

150
00:08:58,800 --> 00:09:00,881
So what?

151
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:03,841
I was able to quell
the Five Princes Rebellion back then,

152
00:09:04,321 --> 00:09:05,480
so I am not afraid now.

153
00:09:06,641 --> 00:09:07,401
Father,

154
00:09:09,441 --> 00:09:10,881
you are the best father.

155
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:19,761
Nian,

156
00:09:21,201 --> 00:09:22,720
Cang Xuan is an emperor.

157
00:09:24,029 --> 00:09:24,641
He...

158
00:09:24,641 --> 00:09:25,401
I know.

159
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:27,920
He doesn't like me,

160
00:09:32,081 --> 00:09:33,600
but I like him.

161
00:09:37,401 --> 00:09:38,521
Marrying him

162
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,720
isn't as happy

163
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,920
as I thought it would be,

164
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,761
but I know

165
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:46,081
if I don't marry him,

166
00:09:47,081 --> 00:09:48,641
I'll never be happy in my life.

167
00:09:49,001 --> 00:09:49,680
Nian.

168
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,240
Father,

169
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,401
don't worry.

170
00:09:54,521 --> 00:09:56,240
I'm not what I used to be anymore.

171
00:09:57,281 --> 00:09:58,800
I still like Cang Xuan,

172
00:09:59,401 --> 00:10:00,841
but he's not everything

173
00:10:01,081 --> 00:10:04,521
to me anymore.

174
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:08,480
I'm not the most important to him.

175
00:10:09,001 --> 00:10:09,800
Similarly,

176
00:10:11,281 --> 00:10:13,281
he's not the most important to me.

177
00:10:15,281 --> 00:10:16,641
If I have to choose between him

178
00:10:17,001 --> 00:10:18,521
and you,

179
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,480
I will choose you.

180
00:10:21,321 --> 00:10:22,800
If I have to choose between our people

181
00:10:23,081 --> 00:10:24,521
and him,

182
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:27,321
I will choose our people.

183
00:10:33,040 --> 00:10:33,761
If that's the case,

184
00:10:36,321 --> 00:10:38,001
don't marry Cang Xuan.

185
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,680
Father,

186
00:10:46,680 --> 00:10:48,800
I know well
Cang Xuan doesn't want to marry me,

187
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,040
but I insist on marrying him.

188
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,841
Because between his happiness

189
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,800
and mine,

190
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,321
I choose to make him unhappy

191
00:10:59,281 --> 00:11:00,201
and make myself happy.

192
00:11:10,201 --> 00:11:10,800
Father,

193
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:13,040
I've grown up.

194
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:14,881
I promise

195
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,720
I will take good care of myself.

196
00:11:27,641 --> 00:11:28,720
If you really don't want

197
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,881
the wedding tomorrow,

198
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,720
we'll find a way to cancel it.

199
00:11:34,720 --> 00:11:35,521
How do we do it?

200
00:11:36,480 --> 00:11:38,800
Tomorrow's wedding
is already known to all the people.

201
00:11:39,961 --> 00:11:41,001
Millions of troops

202
00:11:41,001 --> 00:11:42,800
are guarding the border
between the two kingdoms.

203
00:11:42,961 --> 00:11:44,240
One careless move

204
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:46,560
could lead to great chaos.

205
00:11:48,401 --> 00:11:49,800
I haven't thought it through yet.

206
00:11:50,761 --> 00:11:51,421
But

207
00:11:51,680 --> 00:11:52,920
whatever you don't want to do,

208
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:53,961
I will support you.

209
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,761
Let's figure out a way together.

210
00:11:56,001 --> 00:11:57,521
There must be a way to cancel it.

211
00:12:01,401 --> 00:12:02,600
Aren't you afraid of danger?

212
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:04,381
No.

213
00:12:05,001 --> 00:12:06,040
Since we were little,

214
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:07,920
we've never had a peaceful day.

215
00:12:22,841 --> 00:12:23,521
What number is this?

216
00:12:25,441 --> 00:12:25,961
Six.

217
00:12:37,441 --> 00:12:38,560
Are you messing with me?

218
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:47,881
Tomorrow,

219
00:12:49,881 --> 00:12:51,720
all the people will see

220
00:12:52,281 --> 00:12:54,641
the King of Xiyan joyfully

221
00:12:55,441 --> 00:12:58,040
marry the Princess of Haoling.

222
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,441
Cang Xuan.

223
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,841
I was drunk just now.

224
00:13:06,401 --> 00:13:07,281
Now I am sober.

225
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,281
Things have come to this.

226
00:13:10,321 --> 00:13:11,560
Marrying one more woman

227
00:13:12,281 --> 00:13:13,800
makes no difference.

228
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:19,961
Are you really willing?

229
00:13:20,401 --> 00:13:20,989
Yes.

230
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,081
You said just now that you wanted...

231
00:13:26,281 --> 00:13:27,360
What do you want?

232
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,001
As long as it's something I can do,

233
00:13:29,201 --> 00:13:30,201
I will help you achieve it.

234
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,800
I want...

235
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:35,441
What do you want?

236
00:13:36,641 --> 00:13:37,600
I want...

237
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:51,841
I want us both to be safe and sound.

238
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,201
Cang Xuan,

239
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:07,401
you are the King of Xiyan now.

240
00:14:08,521 --> 00:14:09,120
In the future,

241
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,480
you'll be the master of Dahuang.

242
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:13,360
No one will hurt you again.

243
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,641
Nor will anyone hurt me anymore.

244
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:19,920
Right.

245
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:25,641
We have already reached the summit.

246
00:14:36,244 --> 00:14:40,112
♪Looking back on my old days♪

247
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,120
As usual.

248
00:14:42,961 --> 00:14:44,001
Don't congratulate me.

249
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,841
Don't give me gifts.

250
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:50,961
And don't show up
at the wedding tomorrow.

251
00:14:55,680 --> 00:14:56,281
Alright.

252
00:14:57,001 --> 00:14:57,761
I'm not giving a gift.

253
00:14:58,201 --> 00:14:58,961
Nor will I attend.

254
00:15:00,308 --> 00:15:04,240
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

255
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,800
On Wushen Mountain, you and Auntie

256
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:08,160
loved the Yiqing Garden most.

257
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:11,720
I will build you an identical garden

258
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,841
on Chenrong Mountain.

259
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:16,600
You don't have to.

260
00:15:17,441 --> 00:15:18,720
Jing told me in Qingqiu,

261
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,281
he would build me a Yiqing Garden.

262
00:15:26,164 --> 00:15:28,272
♪All things are dim♪

263
00:15:28,272 --> 00:15:31,472
♪While only your eyes shine bright♪

264
00:15:32,212 --> 00:15:36,944
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

265
00:15:38,164 --> 00:15:40,048
♪Everything seems sad♪

266
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:42,560
Why have these fish
suddenly all run away?

267
00:15:46,001 --> 00:15:49,081
The fish from Wushen Mountain
don't like me being here.

268
00:15:53,001 --> 00:15:53,720
Xuan,

269
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,720
just a few fish.

270
00:15:56,281 --> 00:15:58,001
You've conquered Chenrong Mountain.

271
00:15:58,281 --> 00:16:00,321
Wushen Mountain is no challenge for you.

272
00:16:02,881 --> 00:16:03,641
Will you accompany me?

273
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:04,881
Of course.

274
00:16:05,920 --> 00:16:06,600
I will.

275
00:16:11,764 --> 00:16:13,264
♪Without you♪

276
00:16:13,812 --> 00:16:17,300
♪Even the most beautiful world♪

277
00:16:18,736 --> 00:16:19,920
(Cheng'en Palace, Haoling)

278
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:23,472
♪Is a mess♪

279
00:16:33,881 --> 00:16:35,401
(Sunlight Hall)
With wonderful music,

280
00:16:35,841 --> 00:16:37,600
the phoenix arrives in splendor.

281
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:05,776
♪I climbed mountains♪

282
00:18:06,516 --> 00:18:07,696
♪And crossed rivers♪

283
00:18:08,628 --> 00:18:11,984
♪But I couldn't walk out
of life and death♪

284
00:18:12,848 --> 00:18:14,704
♪I lived through gatherings♪

285
00:18:15,024 --> 00:18:16,528
♪And parting♪

286
00:18:17,264 --> 00:18:20,688
♪But I couldn't walk out
of sorrows and joys♪

