356
00:22:18,440 --> 00:22:19,801
The world is vast

357
00:22:22,921 --> 00:22:24,080
and boundless.

358
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,041
Right.

359
00:22:25,041 --> 00:22:26,200
You are a nine-headed demon.

360
00:22:27,281 --> 00:22:30,360
Do you want to be bound by fate?

361
00:22:30,801 --> 00:22:34,440
Have you not considered making

362
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,240
