366
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:52,041
as an object of trade.

367
00:22:52,840 --> 00:22:53,641
But I see you

368
00:22:54,401 --> 00:22:55,881
as a friend.

369
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,881
Friendship

370
00:23:03,801 --> 00:23:05,281
