371
00:23:06,001 --> 00:23:07,401
I don't think I can rely on it.

372
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:14,720
If Xiyan Cang Xuan knows

373
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,840
we both have a poisonous bug
in our hearts

374
00:23:18,320 --> 00:23:19,600
