390
00:24:00,784 --> 00:24:02,761
You can use the poisonous bug
as leverage against Cang Xuan.

391
00:24:03,921 --> 00:24:04,720
Aren't you afraid

392
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:07,120
I would use the poisonous bug
to scheme against you?

393
00:24:07,921 --> 00:24:08,840
Scheme against me?

394
00:24:13,281 --> 00:24:14,161
I'm looking forward to it.

395
00:24:15,681 --> 00:24:16,240
Xiang Liu,

396
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:17,881
