403
00:24:39,561 --> 00:24:40,401
Yes.

404
00:24:41,521 --> 00:24:42,480
What are you worried about?

405
00:24:43,360 --> 00:24:44,041
Nothing.

406
00:24:45,600 --> 00:24:47,200
I was just taking a walk by the sea,

407
00:24:47,801 --> 00:24:49,080
