about removing the poisonous bug.

409
00:24:52,681 --> 00:24:54,080
Does Xiang Liu have a way?

410
00:24:54,161 --> 00:24:55,041
I guess he does.

411
00:24:55,921 --> 00:24:56,840
Otherwise,

412
00:24:56,840 --> 00:24:58,320
knowing it would
make our lives connected,

413
00:24:58,928 --> 00:25:01,001
