inside him willingly.

414
00:25:01,001 --> 00:25:01,681
But

415
00:25:02,041 --> 00:25:02,801
he didn't tell me.

416
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:06,240
The poisonous bug bothers me

417
00:25:06,480 --> 00:25:07,320
until it's removed.

418
