429
00:25:31,641 --> 00:25:32,521
Don't worry.

430
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,240
I've been studying
medicine and compiling

431
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:35,240
medical books recently.

432
00:25:35,881 --> 00:25:37,440
Since Xiang Liu can remove
the poisonous bug,

433
00:25:37,761 --> 00:25:39,041
I can certainly do it too.

434
00:25:39,561 --> 00:25:41,161
It's just that I need some time.

435
00:25:41,641 --> 00:25:42,200
You're right.

436
00:25:43,001 --> 00:25:44,080
We will definitely find a way.

437
00:26:10,480 --> 00:26:11,600
This place.

438
00:26:13,641 --> 00:26:15,001
Have we been here before?

439
00:26:28,120 --> 00:26:29,041
Chief Tushan,

440
00:26:30,360 --> 00:26:31,561
it was here

441
00:26:31,840 --> 00:26:33,801
where I offered my first kiss,

442
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:35,960
