449
00:27:08,801 --> 00:27:09,641
This time,

450
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,320
it is you who can't dodge.

451
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:04,921
Since ascending to the throne
in my prime,

452
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,561
