you have in mind.

466
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:34,720
Not from the Haoling royal family.

467
00:30:35,681 --> 00:30:36,281
It is

468
00:30:39,641 --> 00:30:41,281
Xiyan Cang Xuan.

469
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:43,677
Your Majesty.

470
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:45,921
Absolutely not!

471
00:30:46,281 --> 00:30:48,200
Xiyan Cang Xuan is the king
