00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:20,281
I will abide by your command.

488
00:31:20,681 --> 00:31:21,245
Good.

489
00:31:22,281 --> 00:31:23,041
Qinglong,

490
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:24,761
