491
00:31:24,921 --> 00:31:26,801
We Qinglong Squad

492
00:31:26,881 --> 00:31:28,440
will abide by your command.

493
00:31:30,801 --> 00:31:32,120
We Xihe Squad

494
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,681
will abide by your command.

495
00:31:34,281 --> 00:31:36,681
