to possess alone.

504
00:31:53,401 --> 00:31:55,200
Cang Xuan of Xiyan

505
00:31:55,401 --> 00:31:56,840
(Father cede the throne to me.)
is sagacious

506
00:31:56,840 --> 00:31:58,240
(I'll try to be a good ruler and not let you down.)
and outstanding.

507
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:01,320
Today, I retire to another palace

508
00:32:01,440 --> 00:32:03,001
