509
00:32:03,080 --> 00:32:04,240
That's all.

510
00:32:29,080 --> 00:32:31,401
You and His Majesty have unified Dahuang

511
00:32:31,561 --> 00:32:32,641
without waging war

512
00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:34,281
or disturbing the people.

513
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:36,720
It is truly a joyous
and congratulatory event.

514
00:32:39,521 --> 00:32:40,801
It is too early

515
00:32:41,281 --> 00:32:42,440
to be happy now.

516
00:32:43,521 --> 00:32:46,600
Cang Xuan
has only nominally unified Haoling.

517
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,600
The Haoling tribes

518
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,561
will not be sincerely convinced.

519
00:32:51,200 --> 00:32:52,001
It is heard

520
00:32:52,320 --> 00:32:54,681
