528
00:33:17,840 --> 00:33:19,960
You don't need to worry.

529
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,120
With His Majesty's wisdom and ability,

530
00:33:22,401 --> 00:33:25,561
he will certainly make
the Haoling court officials convinced.

531
00:33:26,641 --> 00:33:27,240
Right.

532
00:33:28,240 --> 00:33:30,281
