00:34:12,680 --> 00:34:14,240
(and accepted their criticism.)

546
00:34:14,801 --> 00:34:16,121
(As for the treacherous ones)

547
00:34:16,121 --> 00:34:17,880
(who profited from chaos,)

548
00:34:18,121 --> 00:34:19,440
(he suppressed them)

549
00:34:19,801 --> 00:34:21,240
(forcefully.)

550
00:34:22,081 --> 00:34:25,121
