552
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:31,480
(the order has been restored
and the governance has been upright.)

553
00:34:32,281 --> 00:34:33,841
(Haoling has prospered.)

554
00:34:34,200 --> 00:34:36,081
(All are convinced.)

555
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:38,801
(Now,)

556
00:34:39,321 --> 00:34:39,920
(Haoling)

557
00:34:40,240 --> 00:34:41,041
(and Xiyan)

558
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,680
(are truly united.)

559
00:34:44,041 --> 00:34:46,200
(Xiyan Cang Xuan is honored)

560
00:34:46,601 --> 00:34:48,521
