565
00:35:04,601 --> 00:35:05,720
Father, you've worked hard.

566
00:35:08,521 --> 00:35:09,181
Cang Xuan,

567
00:35:10,561 --> 00:35:12,041
I want to ask you for something.

568
00:35:13,041 --> 00:35:13,880
No matter what it is,

569
00:35:14,400 --> 00:35:15,440
as long as you want it,

570
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,200
just take it.

571
00:35:17,601 --> 00:35:18,920
I want Xiyan Mountain.

572
00:35:21,081 --> 00:35:21,725
Father,

573
00:35:23,160 --> 00:35:24,041
there's no need for that.

574
00:35:24,801 --> 00:35:27,321
Father, why do you want that?

575
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:29,561
Now, the situation is settled.

576
00:35:30,561 --> 00:35:31,880
I want to leave Wushen Mountain

577
00:35:32,361 --> 00:35:33,601
and move to Xiyan Mountain.

578
00:35:34,281 --> 00:35:35,001
Why?

579
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:38,720
Father does not want
two rulers in one kingdom,

580
00:35:39,281 --> 00:35:41,081
and he is intent on crushing
all the officials' hopes,

581
00:35:42,281 --> 00:35:45,041
and making everyone acknowledge
only Cang Xuan as the king.

582
00:35:46,081 --> 00:35:47,601
There is also a personal reason.

583
00:35:50,521 --> 00:35:51,361
Xiyan Mountain

584
00:35:51,561 --> 00:35:53,561
is the birthplace
of the Xiyan royal family.

585
00:35:54,121 --> 00:35:56,920
It's of extraordinary significance
to the Xiyan Kingdom.

586
00:35:58,160 --> 00:35:59,240
Becoming the master

587
00:35:59,281 --> 00:36:00,640
is to show the world

588
00:36:01,521 --> 00:36:03,601
my status is the same
as the Great Emperor's

589
00:36:04,680 --> 00:36:08,121
and Haoling is not a submission.

590
00:36:12,081 --> 00:36:12,640
Father,

591
00:36:14,081 --> 00:36:15,281
there's really no need for that.

592
00:36:16,801 --> 00:36:18,440
The climate of Wushen Mountain
and Xiyan Mountain

593
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:19,240
is entirely different.

594
00:36:20,121 --> 00:36:21,321
You may not be able to adapt.

595
00:36:22,256 --> 00:36:23,960
The climate of Chenrong Mountain
and Xiyan Mountain

596
00:36:23,960 --> 00:36:24,880
is also entirely different.

597
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:27,640
Isn't your grandfather
also living well there?

598
00:36:29,001 --> 00:36:30,160
I've heard

599
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:32,920
he's must better
than when he was at Xiyan Mountain.

600
00:36:34,240 --> 00:36:34,761
Father,

601
00:36:36,680 --> 00:36:38,521
how can you bear
to leave Wushen Mountain?

602
00:36:44,001 --> 00:36:45,081
On Wushen Mountain,

603
00:36:45,761 --> 00:36:47,281
the only one I can't bear to part with

604
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,400
is you.

605
00:36:55,361 --> 00:36:56,160
I am tired.

606
00:36:56,601 --> 00:36:58,001
I want to change my way of life

607
00:37:00,281 --> 00:37:01,801
and don't want to stay
in this palace anymore.

608
00:37:06,281 --> 00:37:07,640
Your mother will stay to accompany you.

609
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:09,680
Even when Cang Xuan is not around,

610
00:37:09,841 --> 00:37:10,960
you are not alone.

611
00:37:15,041 --> 00:37:15,601
Cang Xuan,

612
00:37:17,041 --> 00:37:18,880
are you willing
to give Xiyan Mountain to me?

613
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,480
Of course I am willing.

614
00:37:24,281 --> 00:37:25,361
But Father,

615
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:28,200
please recover fully before you leave.

616
00:37:29,121 --> 00:37:29,920
If I stay here,

617
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,601
even if I do not want
to deal with something,

618
00:37:32,601 --> 00:37:33,521
it will still reach my ears

619
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:35,321
and prevent me from resting in peace.

620
00:37:36,321 --> 00:37:37,200
If possible,

621
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,240
I want to leave soon.

622
00:37:40,001 --> 00:37:40,601
Father,

623
00:37:41,121 --> 00:37:43,041
let me accompany you back
to Xiyan Mountain.

624
00:37:43,361 --> 00:37:45,321
It's a good opportunity
to help you recuperate.

625
00:37:48,081 --> 00:37:49,601
With you accompanying Father back,

626
00:37:49,841 --> 00:37:51,081
I will be much more at ease.

627
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,081
Rest assured.

628
00:37:57,321 --> 00:37:58,960
I will definitely arrange it
as soon as possible.

629
00:38:02,128 --> 00:38:05,520
(Sunlight Hall)

630
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:44,841
You're a good king.

631
00:38:47,121 --> 00:38:47,960
In my lifetime,

632
00:38:49,640 --> 00:38:51,440
I am not a good son,

633
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:54,281
a good brother, a good friend

634
00:38:55,321 --> 00:38:56,680
or a good husband.

635
00:38:58,240 --> 00:38:59,841
But I am indeed

636
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:03,240
a good king.

637
00:39:06,801 --> 00:39:07,960
You're a good father.

638
00:39:10,480 --> 00:39:13,400
You're the best father to Nian and me.

639
00:39:36,001 --> 00:39:37,880
Greetings, Your Majesty.

640
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,001
What are you here for?

641
00:39:41,601 --> 00:39:42,240
Are you still angry

642
00:39:42,240 --> 00:39:43,601
about the matter
of the Queen of Haoling?

643
00:39:45,361 --> 00:39:46,680
It was my fault for not informing you

644
00:39:46,680 --> 00:39:47,601
in advance.

645
00:39:48,601 --> 00:39:50,121
I've come specially to apologize.

646
00:39:51,361 --> 00:39:52,160
To apologize?

647
00:39:53,841 --> 00:39:55,041
You did a lot

648
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,640
to help His Majesty marry

649
00:39:57,720 --> 00:39:59,160
the Princess of Haoling.

650
00:39:59,561 --> 00:40:02,400
Now, your fame
in the court is resounding.

651
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:04,321
I can't afford

652
00:40:05,281 --> 00:40:07,081
your apology.

653
00:40:08,121 --> 00:40:08,669
Your Majesty,

654
00:40:09,456 --> 00:40:11,920
the marriage alliance between the two
royal families of Xiyan and Haoling

655
00:40:11,920 --> 00:40:13,480
has averted a war

656
00:40:13,801 --> 00:40:15,640
between the two kingdoms
that may last for decades

657
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:16,920
or even hundreds of years.

658
00:40:17,601 --> 00:40:19,041
The people will all be grateful to you.

659
00:40:19,041 --> 00:40:19,680
Enough!

660
00:40:21,281 --> 00:40:22,521
Save your principles

661
00:40:22,521 --> 00:40:24,001
for the court session.

662
00:40:24,761 --> 00:40:26,521
I am not your peer or subordinate.

663
00:40:27,601 --> 00:40:28,240
I am

664
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:32,001
your sister of the same mother.

665
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:33,561
Xinyue,

666
00:40:34,321 --> 00:40:35,321
I'm doing this for your good.

667
00:40:36,121 --> 00:40:37,680
The Queen of Haoling lives
at Wushen Mountain.

668
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:38,761
You can't see her at all.

669
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:41,121
She has no impact on your status.

670
00:40:41,200 --> 00:40:42,720
For my good?

671
00:40:45,081 --> 00:40:46,400
You and father,

672
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:49,160
for what you call the clan's interest,

673
00:40:49,361 --> 00:40:51,521
for your own high positions,

674
00:40:51,521 --> 00:40:53,240
have sacrificed me once again.

675
00:40:56,561 --> 00:40:58,480
Putting on airs.

676
00:40:59,521 --> 00:41:01,081
Utterly hypocritical.

677
00:41:01,561 --> 00:41:02,640
Just scold me

678
00:41:02,640 --> 00:41:03,440
if you want.

679
00:41:03,640 --> 00:41:04,640
Don't bring Father into this.

680
00:41:06,361 --> 00:41:07,640
I warned you about this from the start

681
00:41:09,041 --> 00:41:10,761
His Majesty carried
the whole world in his mind.

682
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:13,200
If you wanted a devoted husband,

683
00:41:13,200 --> 00:41:14,200
don't marry His Majesty.

684
00:41:15,480 --> 00:41:16,960
This was your own choice.

685
00:41:17,720 --> 00:41:19,720
It wasn't me or Father
who forced you to become the queen.

686
00:41:22,160 --> 00:41:23,521
Without me and father,

687
00:41:24,208 --> 00:41:26,480
would someone willful and selfish
like you secure your position?

688
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,480
Get out of my sight!

689
00:41:31,720 --> 00:41:33,880
I will no longer need
your concern in the future.

690
00:42:00,368 --> 00:42:03,312
(Base Camp of Chenrong Army)

691
00:42:04,121 --> 00:42:04,640
One.

692
00:42:06,200 --> 00:42:06,749
Two.

693
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:08,960
Three.

694
00:42:10,200 --> 00:42:10,761
Four.

695
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,053
Five.

696
00:42:14,321 --> 00:42:15,005
Six.

697
00:42:18,121 --> 00:42:18,761
Mr. Xiang.

698
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,121
Starting today,

699
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,960
add an extra portion
of meat to everyone.

700
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:28,801
You've gathered more provisions.

701
00:42:29,361 --> 00:42:31,041
Let me say thank you
on behalf of everyone.

702
00:42:33,041 --> 00:42:33,693
Three.

703
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,480
Four.

704
00:42:37,001 --> 00:42:37,661
Five.

705
00:42:40,081 --> 00:42:40,701
Six.

706
00:42:42,440 --> 00:42:43,216
Tell me.

707
00:42:43,361 --> 00:42:45,081
Does our perseverance make sense?

708
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,440
No matter the obstacles,

709
00:42:55,200 --> 00:42:55,960
I shall go forth.

710
00:43:19,098 --> 00:43:22,330
♪Looking back on my old days♪

711
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:27,898
♪I was unruffled
with no sorrow and soreness♪

712
00:43:29,978 --> 00:43:34,778
♪In my chaotic life,
I failed to meet your gaze♪

713
00:43:37,914 --> 00:43:40,186
♪Only emptiness remained♪

714
00:43:43,130 --> 00:43:46,202
♪Enduring all things in my life♪

715
00:43:48,051 --> 00:43:52,442
♪I valued all but indifferent
to wealth and fame♪

716
00:43:53,978 --> 00:43:59,451
♪Basking in the sun,
I couldn't feel your sunlight♪

717
00:44:00,402 --> 00:44:06,234
♪All I feel is a painful heat wave♪

718
00:44:09,082 --> 00:44:13,818
♪All things are dim,
while only your eyes shine bright♪

719
00:44:15,130 --> 00:44:19,642
♪I'll follow my heart
and go to chase the sun far away♪

720
00:44:21,082 --> 00:44:27,034
♪Everything seems sad,
while only your brows raise in delight♪

721
00:44:27,811 --> 00:44:32,122
♪I'm waiting for you
to enjoy the scenery at night♪

722
00:44:33,114 --> 00:44:38,080
♪You came with wind and rain,
while left with my four seasons♪

723
00:44:39,072 --> 00:44:43,680
♪All is bleak without you♪

724
00:44:45,018 --> 00:44:50,624
♪It began like a tornado,
and went away leaving only dust♪

725
00:44:51,738 --> 00:45:02,752
♪Without you,
even the most beautiful world is a mess♪
